use Sise\CoreBundle\Form\Type\NomenclatureType; use Symfony\Bundle\FrameworkBundle\Controller\Controller; use Symfony\Component\HttpFoundation\Request; use Symfony\Component\HttpFoundation\Response; use Symfony\Component\Routing\Annotation\Route;  class AdminController extends Controller {     /**      * @Route("/admin", name="admin")      */     public function index()     {         return $this->render('SiseCoreBundle:Admin:index.html.twig');     }      /**      * @Route("/admin/nomenclature", name="admin_nomenclature")      */     public function nomenclature()     {         $form = $this->createForm(new NomenclatureType());          return $this->render('SiseCoreBundle:Admin:nomenclature.html.twig', array(             'form' => $form->createView()         ));     }      /**      * @Route("/admin/nomenclature/generate", name="admin_nomenclature_generate")      */     public function generateNomenclature()     {         $form = $this->createForm(new NomenclatureType());         $request = $this->getRequest();          if ($request->getMethod() == 'POST') {             $form->bind($request);              if ($form->isValid()) {                 $entity = new Nomenclature();                 $entity->setDescription($form->get('description')->getData());                 $entity->setParent($form->get('parent')->getData());                 $entity->setLevel($form->get('level')->getData());                 $entity->setCode($form->get('code')->getData());                 $entity->setCreatedAt($this->get('kernel')->getCacheDir());                 $entity->setUpdatedAt($this->get('kernel')->getCacheDir());                 $entity->setStatus(1);                  $em = $this->getDoctrine()->getManager();                 $em->persist($entity);                 $em->flush();                  return $this->redirect($this->generateUrl('admin_nomenclature_list'));             }         }          return $this->render('SiseCoreBundle:Admin:nomenclature.html.twig', array(             'form' => $form->createView()         ));     } }
